criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  age ≥ 45 and ≤ 90 years;

          -  patients with severe (70-99%) carotid stenosis, diagnosed with color doppler
             echography or angio-MRI or angiography;

          -  written informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  carotid stenosis <70% at carotid bifurcation or diagnosed with color doppler
             echography or angio-MRI or angiography;

          -  severe neoplasia;

          -  participation to other clinical trial, ongoing or terminated less than one month
             before enrolment in this study.
